ption': 'Optimized for latency on MI325X using fp16 precision', 'profileId': 'vllm-mi325x-fp16-tp1-latency'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI325X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'metric': 'throughput', 'description': 'Optimized for throughput on MI325X using fp16 precision', 'profileId': 'vllm-mi325x-fp16-tp1-throughput'}]"}	amdenterpriseai-aim-mistralai-mistral-small-3-2-24-0.8.5-0139f1	amdenterpriseai/aim-mistralai-mistral-small-3-2-24b-instruct-2506:0.8.5	Ready
6450ee8d-28ed-4b50-a39b-103fc5b8a523	2026-03-17 12:31:36.107967+00	2026-03-17 12:35:04.380899+00	system	system	{"com.amd.aim.title": "meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.model.tags": "text-generation, chat, instruction", "com.amd.aim.model.source": "https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.release.notes": "", "com.amd.aim.model.variants": "amd/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct-FP8-KV, meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.description.full": "The Meta Llama 3.1 collection, released by Meta on July 23, 2024, is a set of multilingual large language models available in 8B, 70B, and 405B parameter sizes. The models are offered in both pretrained and instruction-tuned versions, with the latter being optimized for dialogue use cases. Built on an auto-regressive transformer architecture with Grouped-Query Attention (GQA), the tuned models are refined using Supervised Fine-Tuning (SFT) and Reinforcement Learning with Human Feedback (RLHF). Llama 3.1 is intended for commercial and research applications. The instruction-tuned models are designed for assistant-like chat, while the pretrained models can be adapted for various natural language generation tasks. The custom commercial license also allows for using the model's output for synthetic data generation and distillation to improve other models.", "com.amd.aim.hfToken.required": "True", "org.opencontainers.image.title": "meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.model.canonicalName": "meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct", "org.opencontainers.image.source": "https://github.com/silogen/aim-build", "org.opencontainers.image.vendor": "AMD", "org.opencontainers.image.authors": "", "org.opencontainers.image.created": "2025-11-11T10:45:11Z", "org.opencontainers.image.version": "", "org.opencontainers.image.licenses": "llama3.1, MIT", "org.opencontainers.image.ref.name": "ubuntu", "org.opencontainers.image.revision": "bdba5c8c0a6be5962f098fa4bbe0ecbce9fdc07a", "org.opencontainers.image.description": "Instruction-tuned version of Llama 3.1 8B optimized for chat and instruction following.", "org.opencontainers.image.documentation": "", "com.amd.aim.model.recommendedDeployments": "{'gpuModel': 'MI300X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp8', 'metric': 'latency', 'description': 'Optimized for latency on MI300X using fp8 precision'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI300X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp8', 'metric': 'throughput', 'description': 'Optimized for throughput on MI300X using fp8 precision'}"}	amdenterpriseai-aim-meta-llama-llama-3-1-8b-instru-0.8.4-590b84	amdenterpriseai/aim-meta-llama-llama-3-1-8b-instruct:0.8.4	Ready
6828d12d-eb90-475d-89ce-902e19dd2500	2026-03-17 12:31:36.107993+00	2026-03-17 12:35:04.380945+00	system	system	{"maintainer": "dl.mlsedevops@amd.com", "com.amd.aim.title": "Llama 3.3 70B Instruct", "com.amd.aim.model.tags": "text-generation, chat, instruction", "com.amd.aim.model.source": "https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.release.notes": "", "com.amd.aim.model.variants": "amd/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-FP8-KV, meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.model.publisher": "Meta", "com.amd.aim.description.full": "Llama 3.3 70B Instruct is a multilingual large language model from Meta with 70 billion parameters. It is an auto-regressive language model using an optimized transformer architecture with Grouped-Query Attention (GQA). The instruction-tuned version uses supervised fine-tuning (SFT) and reinforcement learning with human feedback (RLHF) to align with human preferences for helpfulness and safety. The model supports multilingual dialogue across 8 languages (English, German, French, Italian, Portuguese, Hindi, Spanish, and Thai) with a 128k token context length. Pre-trained on over 15 trillion tokens of publicly available data with a knowledge cutoff of December 2023. Intended for assistant-like chat, with support for tool use, synthetic data generation, and model distillation.", "com.amd.aim.hfToken.required": "True", "org.opencontainers.image.title": "meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct", "com.amd.aim.model.canonicalName": "meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct", "org.opencontainers.image.source": "https://github.com/silogen/aim-build", "org.opencontainers.image.vendor": "AMD", "org.opencontainers.image.authors": "", "org.opencontainers.image.created": "2026-03-04T09:15:29Z", "org.opencontainers.image.version": "", "org.opencontainers.image.licenses": "llama3.3, MIT", "org.opencontainers.image.ref.name": "ubuntu", "org.opencontainers.image.revision": "268e89c5c4c0dcb4edfd448a8e13606699cac497", "org.opencontainers.image.description": "Multilingual 70B parameter instruction-tuned language model for dialogue use cases.", "org.opencontainers.image.documentation": "", "com.amd.aim.model.recommendedDeployments": "[{'gpuModel': 'MI300X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp8', 'metric': 'latency', 'description': 'Optimized for latency on MI300X using fp8 precision'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI300X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp8', 'metric': 'throughput', 'description': 'Optimized for throughput on MI300X using fp8 precision'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI325X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'metric': 'latency', 'description': 'Optimized for latency on MI325X using fp8 precision', 'profileId': 'vllm-mi325x-fp8-tp1-latency'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI325X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'metric': 'throughput', 'description': 'Optimized for throughput on MI325X using fp8 precision', 'profileId': 'vllm-mi325x-fp8-tp1-throughput'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI350X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp4', 'metric': 'latency', 'description': 'Optimized for latency on MI350X using fp4 precision'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI350X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'metric': 'throughput', 'description': 'Optimized for throughput on MI350X using fp4 precision', 'profileId': 'vllm-mi350x-mxfp4-tp1-throughput'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI355X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp4', 'metric': 'latency', 'description': 'Optimized for latency on MI355X using fp4 precision'}, {'gpuModel': 'MI355X', 'gpuCount': 1, 'precision': 'fp8', 'metric': 'throughput', 'description': 'Optimized for throughput on MI355X using fp8 precision'}]"}	amdenterpriseai-aim-meta-llama-llama-3-3-70b-inst-0.10.0-39e309	amdenterpriseai/aim-meta-llama-llama-3-3-70b-instruct:0.10.0	Ready
